          "cleaned_contract_text": "Hello Legal Team, I hope you're doing well. Please find attached the Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) for the upcoming partnership between Acme Corp and your organization. We would appreciate it if you could review the document and confirm whether the terms are acceptable or if any revisions are required. Key points to note: - The agreement covers confidential information related to our joint product development initiative. - The NDA term is set for 3 years. - Jurisdiction is currently listed as Delaware, USA. If possible, please share your feedback by the end of this week so we can proceed with the partnership discussions. Let me know if you need any clarification from our side. Best regards, John Smith Head of Partnerships Acme Corp john.smith@acmecorp.com +1 415 555 9823"
