          "html": "<div dir=\"ltr\">Hello Legal Team,<br><br>I hope you&#39;re doing well.<br><br>Please find attached the Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) for the upcoming partnership between Acme Corp and your organization.<br><br>We would appreciate it if you could review the document and confirm whether the terms are acceptable or if any revisions are required.<br><br>Key points to note:<br>- The agreement covers confidential information related to our joint product development initiative.<br>- The NDA term is set for 3 years.<br>- Jurisdiction is currently listed as Delaware, USA.<br><br>If possible, please share your feedback by the end of this week so we can proceed with the partnership discussions.<br><br>Let me know if you need any clarification from our side.<br><br>Best regards,<br><br>John Smith  <br>Head of Partnerships  <br>Acme Corp  <br><a href=\"mailto:john.smith@acmecorp.com\" target=\"_blank\">john.smith@acmecorp.com</a>  <br>+1 415 555 9823</div>\n",
          "text": "Hello Legal Team,\n\nI hope you're doing well.\n\nPlease find attached the Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) for the upcoming\npartnership between Acme Corp and your organization.\n\nWe would appreciate it if you could review the document and confirm whether\nthe terms are acceptable or if any revisions are required.\n\nKey points to note:\n- The agreement covers confidential information related to our joint\nproduct development initiative.\n- The NDA term is set for 3 years.\n- Jurisdiction is currently listed as Delaware, USA.\n\nIf possible, please share your feedback by the end of this week so we can\nproceed with the partnership discussions.\n\nLet me know if you need any clarification from our side.\n\nBest regards,\n\nJohn Smith\nHead of Partnerships\nAcme Corp\njohn.smith@acmecorp.com\n+1 415 555 9823\n",
          "textAsHtml": "<p>Hello Legal Team,</p><p>I hope you&apos;re doing well.</p><p>Please find attached the Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) for the upcoming<br/>partnership between Acme Corp and your organization.</p><p>We would appreciate it if you could review the document and confirm whether<br/>the terms are acceptable or if any revisions are required.</p><p>Key points to note:<br/>- The agreement covers confidential information related to our joint<br/>product development initiative.<br/>- The NDA term is set for 3 years.<br/>- Jurisdiction is currently listed as Delaware, USA.</p><p>If possible, please share your feedback by the end of this week so we can<br/>proceed with the partnership discussions.</p><p>Let me know if you need any clarification from our side.</p><p>Best regards,</p><p>John Smith<br/>Head of Partnerships<br/>Acme Corp<br/><a href=\"mailto:john.smith@acmecorp.com\">john.smith@acmecorp.com</a><br/>+1 415 555 9823</p>",
